{"tid":2145303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有流亡手足見到呢張相差d哭𠹌左","createTime":"2020-08-08T03:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T04:33:41.000Z","uid":232848,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0abf3676227b395c4c77e7e6d29dfef8a5371f5b","tid":2145303,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mhPYLEj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmhPYLEj.jpg&h=5449e621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">上年11月完全估唔到有命可以睇到港共比美帝制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係有好多手足已經無機會見到</span><br />\n<br />\nbtw 好想食返香港既牛腩河<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【 願最大功勞，歸前線手足。 】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n念念不忘，必有迴響。<br />\n<br />\n誠然，理大圍城一役，係香港人輸得最慘烈既一仗。但今日既制裁中，唯一一件個別抗爭事件被列作制裁原因，就係理大圍城呢一場反人道戰役。<br />\n<br />\n係大家開香檳同時，請藉呢個機會，向每一位為呢個城巿企過上抗爭前線既手足致謝。亦唔止係理大，仲有中大、金鐘、旺角，每一區每一次抗爭嘅手足。比佢地知道，佢地咁多既付出，並唔係白費；香港人，亦會永遠記得、永遠感謝。<br />\n<br />\n今日既成果，係由佢地既血汗、自由、無私既犧牲去換返黎。佢地好多好多人，今日仍然身陷囹圄或有案在身。我地離成功還很遠，但我地會為佢地行落去，直到佢地係自由既新香港昂首而立，得到應得既正名。<br />\n//"},{"pid":"801f877237863ed7c5c6994f68b8d3ab58919d5c","tid":2145303,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe616ef037892c827f3069045be10b2196b80fe","tid":2145303,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081709769d26814603e24fff80d4b201fae1fdef","tid":2145303,"uid":118080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"等手足返嚟同我哋一齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e1326f4856b221fa2efe287fcc6c758ab53c63","tid":2145303,"uid":293937,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸手足"},{"pid":"64bbc7e42f16f9f42801bc2817cde628055829a6","tid":2145303,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"081709769d26814603e24fff80d4b201fae1fdef","tid":2145303,"uid":118080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"等手足返嚟同我哋一齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb17e3b99e2aefc8fc938490819712628797c57","tid":2145303,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"國際線要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到五眼跟機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}